---
layout: base.njk
title: "FrenzyZone — D2R Duo Leveling Guide"
---

{# ========== HERO ========== #}
<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-icons">
      <svg class="hero-class-icon barb-icon"><use href="#icon-barb"/></svg>
      <svg class="hero-class-icon necro-icon"><use href="#icon-necro"/></svg>
      <div class="hero-heart">
        <svg class="heart-icon heart-whole"><use href="#icon-heart"/></svg>
        <svg class="heart-icon heart-broken"><use href="#icon-heart-broken"/></svg>
        <svg class="heart-icon heart-affair"><use href="#icon-heart-arrow"/></svg>
      </div>
      <svg class="hero-class-icon zon-icon"><use href="#icon-zon"/></svg>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Diablo II Resurrected &mdash; Duo Leveling Guide</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      <span class="hero-line hero-line-barb"><span class="barb-text">Frenzy</span></span>
      <span class="hero-line hero-line-necro"><span class="necro-text">Manfred</span></span>
      <span class="hero-line hero-line-mid"><span class="amp">&amp;</span></span>
      <span class="hero-line hero-line-zon"><span class="zon-text">Javazon</span></span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline hero-tagline-default">"Two weapons, one storm &mdash; nothing survives."</p>
    <p class="hero-tagline hero-tagline-affair">"The dead rise, the lightning strikes &mdash; Manfred sends his regards."</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#synergy">Begin the Journey</a>
    </div>
    <div class="divorce-toggle">
      <p class="divorce-label">Divorce Mode</p>
      <div class="divorce-buttons">
        <button class="divorce-btn" data-mode="barb" title="Divorce Mode: Male Edition">
          <svg class="divorce-icon"><use href="#icon-barb"/></svg>
          <span>Male Edition</span>
        </button>
        <button class="divorce-btn" data-mode="zon" title="Divorce Mode: Female Edition">
          <svg class="divorce-icon"><use href="#icon-zon"/></svg>
          <span>Female Edition</span>
        </button>
        <button class="divorce-btn affair-btn" data-mode="affair" title="Affair with Manfred">
          <svg class="divorce-icon"><use href="#icon-necro"/></svg>
          <span>Affair with Manfred</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-indicator"><span></span></div>
</header>

<div class="divider"></div>

{# ========== SYNERGY ========== #}
<section id="synergy">
  {% include "components/section-header.njk" ignore missing %}
  {% set label = "Why This Duo Works" %}
  {% set title = "Unholy Synergy" %}
  {% set desc = "Physical devastation meets elemental fury. The Frenzy Barbarian carves through single targets and tanks the frontline while the Javazon annihilates packs with lightning and piercing javelins." %}
  <div class="section-header">
    <svg class="section-icon"><use href="#icon-star"/></svg>
    <p class="section-label">{{ label }}</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">{{ title }}</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
    <p class="section-desc">{{ desc }}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="synergy-grid">
    <div class="synergy-card barb">
      <h3><svg class="class-icon"><use href="#icon-barb"/></svg>{{ synergy.barb.title }}</h3>
      <ul>
        {%- for point in synergy.barb.points %}
        <li>{{ point }}</li>
        {%- endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="synergy-card necro">
      <h3><svg class="class-icon"><use href="#icon-necro"/></svg>{{ synergy.necro.title }}</h3>
      <ul>
        {%- for point in synergy.necro.points %}
        <li>{{ point }}</li>
        {%- endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="synergy-connector">
      <span class="line"></span>
      <span class="plus">+</span>
      <span class="line"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="synergy-card zon">
      <h3><svg class="class-icon"><use href="#icon-zon"/></svg>{{ synergy.zon.title }}</h3>
      <ul>
        {%- for point in synergy.zon.points %}
        <li>{{ point }}</li>
        {%- endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="synergy-bottom synergy-bottom-default">
      <h3>Combined Strengths</h3>
      <p>{{ synergy.combined.summary }}</p>
      <div class="synergy-highlights">
        {%- for stat in synergy.combined.stats %}
        <div class="synergy-stat">
          <span class="value">{{ stat.value }}</span>
          <span class="label">{{ stat.label }}</span>
        </div>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="synergy-bottom synergy-bottom-affair">
      <h3>Unholy Union</h3>
      <p>{{ synergy.combined_affair.summary }}</p>
      <div class="synergy-highlights">
        {%- for stat in synergy.combined_affair.stats %}
        <div class="synergy-stat">
          <span class="value">{{ stat.value }}</span>
          <span class="label">{{ stat.label }}</span>
        </div>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

{# ========== LEVELING TIMELINE ========== #}
<section id="leveling">
  <div class="section-header">
    <svg class="section-icon"><use href="#icon-scroll"/></svg>
    <p class="section-label">Act by Act</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Leveling Path</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
    <p class="section-desc">From Blood Moor to the Worldstone Chamber. Follow this timeline to optimize skill allocation and progression for both characters.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline">
    {%- for phase in leveling %}
    {% set phase = phase %}
    {% include "components/timeline-phase.njk" %}
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

{# ========== GEAR ========== #}
<section id="gear">
  <div class="section-header">
    <svg class="section-icon"><use href="#icon-weapon"/></svg>
    <p class="section-label">Equipment</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Gear Progression</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
    <p class="section-desc">From rags to riches. Gear recommendations for each difficulty tier, from budget options to best-in-slot.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="gear-tabs">
    <button class="gear-tab active" data-tab="normal">Normal</button>
    <button class="gear-tab" data-tab="nightmare">Nightmare</button>
    <button class="gear-tab" data-tab="hell">Hell / Endgame</button>
  </div>

  {%- for tier, tierData in gear %}
  <div class="gear-panel{{ ' active' if loop.first }}" id="gear-{{ tier }}">
    <div class="gear-grid">
      {% set data = tierData.barb %}
      {% set side = "barb" %}
      {% include "components/gear-column.njk" %}
      {% set data = tierData.necro %}
      {% set side = "necro" %}
      {% include "components/gear-column.njk" %}
      {% set data = tierData.zon %}
      {% set side = "zon" %}
      {% include "components/gear-column.njk" %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {%- endfor %}
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

{# ========== ATTRIBUTES ========== #}
<section id="attributes">
  <div class="section-header">
    <svg class="section-icon"><use href="#icon-strength"/></svg>
    <p class="section-label">Stat Points</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Attribute Allocation</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
    <p class="section-desc">Where to put your stat points. The short version: enough Strength and Dex for gear, everything else into Vitality, never touch Energy.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="dual-panel">
    {% set data = attributes.barb %}
    {% set side = "barb" %}
    {% include "components/stat-block.njk" %}
    {% set data = attributes.necro %}
    {% set side = "necro" %}
    {% include "components/stat-block.njk" %}
    {% set data = attributes.zon %}
    {% set side = "zon" %}
    {% include "components/stat-block.njk" %}
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

{# ========== MERCENARIES ========== #}
<section id="mercs">
  <div class="section-header">
    <svg class="section-icon"><use href="#icon-armor"/></svg>
    <p class="section-label">Hired Help</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Mercenaries</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
    <p class="section-desc">Your mercs are your third and fourth party members. Gear them well and coordinate their auras for maximum duo synergy.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="dual-panel">
    {% set data = mercs.barb %}
    {% set side = "barb" %}
    {% include "components/merc-card.njk" %}
    {% set data = mercs.necro %}
    {% set side = "necro" %}
    {% include "components/merc-card.njk" %}
    {% set data = mercs.zon %}
    {% set side = "zon" %}
    {% include "components/merc-card.njk" %}
    <div class="merc-strategy merc-strategy-default">
      <h3>{{ mercs.duo_strategy.title }}</h3>
      <ul>
        {%- for point in mercs.duo_strategy.points %}
        <li>{{ point }}</li>
        {%- endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="merc-strategy merc-strategy-affair">
      <h3>{{ mercs.duo_strategy_affair.title }}</h3>
      <ul>
        {%- for point in mercs.duo_strategy_affair.points %}
        <li>{{ point }}</li>
        {%- endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

{# ========== CHARMS ========== #}
<section id="charms">
  <div class="section-header">
    <svg class="section-icon"><use href="#icon-charm"/></svg>
    <p class="section-label">Inventory</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Charms</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
    <p class="section-desc">Your inventory is extra gear slots. Fill them wisely &mdash; the right charms can double your damage and survivability.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="dual-panel">
    {% set data = charms.barb %}
    {% set side = "barb" %}
    {% include "components/charm-card.njk" %}
    {% set data = charms.necro %}
    {% set side = "necro" %}
    {% include "components/charm-card.njk" %}
    {% set data = charms.zon %}
    {% set side = "zon" %}
    {% include "components/charm-card.njk" %}
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

{# ========== FARMING ========== #}
<section id="farming">
  <div class="section-header">
    <svg class="section-icon"><use href="#icon-map"/></svg>
    <p class="section-label">Where to Farm</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Farming Guide</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
    <p class="section-desc">The best zones and bosses to farm as a Frenzy Barb + Javazon duo, ordered by priority. Get your gear, get your runes, get your levels.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="farm-filters">
    <button class="farm-filter active" data-filter="all">All Zones</button>
    <button class="farm-filter" data-filter="essential">Essential</button>
    <button class="farm-filter" data-filter="high">High Priority</button>
    <button class="farm-filter" data-filter="medium">Medium</button>
  </div>

  <div class="farm-list">
    {%- for farm in farming %}
    {% set farm = farm %}
    {% include "components/farm-card.njk" %}
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

{# ========== TIPS ========== #}
<section id="tips">
  <div class="section-header">
    <svg class="section-icon"><use href="#icon-campfire"/></svg>
    <p class="section-label">Party Play</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Duo Strategies</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
    <p class="section-desc">Coordination tips to maximize your duo's efficiency from Normal through Hell.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="tips-grid tips-grid-default">
    {%- for tip in tips.default %}
    {% set tip = tip %}
    {% include "components/tip-card.njk" %}
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="tips-grid tips-grid-affair">
    {%- for tip in tips.affair %}
    {% set tip = tip %}
    {% include "components/tip-card.njk" %}
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
